{"tid":147142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉芬拿:拜仁敗給雲加實在無辦法 雲加太不可思議了","createTime":"2017-03-07T15:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T05:14:25.000Z","uid":9581,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33e49ce027b2ffa4a10962337b6c50adc0dcbf22","tid":147142,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"歐聯十六強次回合，拜仁隊長拿姆停賽，由聖拉芬代替拿姆出任右閘，但賽事開始只有兩分半鐘，阿仙奴從左邊一個突襲先入一球，最终以6:0打敗拜仁，晉級八強<br />\n賽後聖拉芬表示「敗給雲加實在無辦法，雲加太不可思議了。從第一個入球開始，我已經深深明白到打敗雲加是不可能的，雲加戰術太美妙了，就好比藝術品一樣，我們沒有辦法看透，沒法進攻，更沒法防守，我今日沒有成功防守過一次，我在雲加面前就好像一個肉便器。能夠敗在雲加手上，我感到非常光榮，今天輸6球對我以言並不可恥，因為對手係個連神都會羨慕既智者。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預料賽後就會出現類似上述既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be397d209993e0febe7b4b9d60d37fda297c73d","tid":147142,"uid":21851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:51:20.000Z","msg":"黑洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b93d5107f4c105816e3f1eee27f239f641c47c","tid":147142,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"今場阿狗大炒我拜6比2啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178cdd7ae99c944623b7a57b1ba7b4dff209a045","tid":147142,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"第一次支持泥清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d0ec675e0b2beae5da7250f36de77cb8f29145","tid":147142,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"一諗到下季成季都有得睇聖拉芬就好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b34a9f04f747f2f3f786e98c084d0d9445089b","tid":147142,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一諗到下季成季都有得睇聖拉芬就好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以買人㗎<img src=\"/asse